      "text": "群兽向我奔来，可要将我踏成肉泥了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1078,
      "line_end": 1103
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老妇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1078,
      "line_end": 1103
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，大伙儿快走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1078,
      "line_end": 1103
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1104,
      "line_end": 1129
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大头鬼皱眉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1104,
      "line_end": 1129
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄听他说话语音中恨恶愤怒之意极深，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1104,
      "line_end": 1129
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西山一窟鬼",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1168,
      "line_end": 1183
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那讨债鬼本使镔铁牌，只因他再细微的怨仇也必报复，从不放过一个小小得罪他之人，武林中送了他一个外号叫作",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1168,
      "line_end": 1183
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二姊，我来助你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1184,
      "line_end": 1209
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们干什么？诡计伤人，算什么好汉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1184,
      "line_end": 1209
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "史叔刚向她点了点头，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1210,
      "line_end": 1233
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笑脸鬼道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1210,
      "line_end": 1233
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这大个子中了诡计，甚是可怜！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1234,
      "line_end": 1259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "翻身站起，伸手背揉了揉眼睛，见四鬼围攻史叔刚，大声叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1234,
      "line_end": 1259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1234,
      "line_end": 1259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红俏鬼接住了皮帽，立即掷给长须鬼，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1278,
      "line_end": 1301
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "长须鬼却将皮帽抛在笑脸鬼头上，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1278,
      "line_end": 1301
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神雕侠到了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 1278,
      "line_end": 1301
    }
